{"content": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>YouGamble2 — Premier League Pattern Analyzer</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>⚽</text></svg>">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0d0d1a;
      --surface: #16162e;
      --card: #1e1e3a;
      --border: #2a2a50;
      --accent: #ff4757;
      --accent2: #2ed573;
      --gold: #ffa502;
      --purple: #a855f7;
      --blue: #3b82f6;
      --text: #eee;
      --text2: #888;
      --prem: #37003c;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 16px; }

    header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--prem), #1a0050);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #5a0080;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--gold));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    header p { color: #bbb; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    header .subtitle {
      color: var(--text2);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* Controls panel */
    .controls {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 700px) { .controls { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .control-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px;
    }
    .control-card h3 {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text2);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .control-card select, .control-card input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }
    .control-card select:focus, .control-card input:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: var(--accent);
    }
    .control-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      align-items: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    .control-row select { width: auto; flex: 1; min-width: 80px; margin-bottom: 0; }
    .control-row input[type="number"] { width: 60px; flex: none; margin-bottom: 0; }
    .control-row label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text2); white-space: nowrap; }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: white;
      padding: 1px 10px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .badge-purple { background: var(--purple); }
    .badge-green { background: var(--accent2); }

    /* Buttons */
    button {
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: white; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #d43650; }
    .btn-secondary { background: var(--card); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border) !important; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--surface); }
    .btn-success { background: var(--accent2); color: white; }
    .btn-success:hover { background: #26c462; }
    .btn-purple { background: var(--purple); color: white; }
    .btn-purple:hover { background: #9333ea; }
    .btn-blue { background: var(--blue); color: white; }
    .btn-blue:hover { background: #2563eb; }
    .btn-sm { padding: 5px 12px; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    .btn-danger { background: #dc2626; color: white; }
    .btn-danger:hover { background: #b91c1c; }

    /* Save patterns button */
    .pattern-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* Main tabs */
    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 4px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .tab-btn {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 10px;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text2);
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
    .tab-btn.active { background: var(--card); color: var(--text); border: 1px solid var(--border); }

    /* Saved patterns list */
    .saved-patterns {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .saved-pattern-pill {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }
    .saved-pattern-pill:hover { border-color: var(--accent); }
    .saved-pattern-pill.active { border-color: var(--accent2); background: rgba(46,213,115,0.1); }
    .saved-pattern-pill .remove {
      color: var(--text2);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .saved-pattern-pill .remove:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* Content regions */
    .tab-content { display: none; }
    .tab-content.active { display: block; }

    /* Team stats card */
    .team-stats {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .team-stats-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .team-stats-header h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
    .team-stats-header .meta { color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.8rem; }

    .match-strip {
      display: flex;
      gap: 6px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .match-chip {
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .chip-win { background: #1b5e20; color: #81c784; }
    .chip-draw { background: #555; color: #ccc; }
    .chip-loss { background: #b71c1c; color: #ef9a9a; }
    .chip-unknown { background: #333; color: #777; }

    /* Pattern results */
    .results-panel {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .results-panel h3 {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .results-panel h3 .count {
      color: var(--text2);
      font-weight: normal;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .result-stat-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(110px, 1fr));
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .result-stat {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .result-stat .num {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }
    .result-stat .lbl {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--text2);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .num-green { color: var(--accent2); }
    .num-red { color: var(--accent); }
    .num-gold { color: var(--gold); }
    .num-purple { color: var(--purple); }
    .num-blue { color: var(--blue); }

    .distribution-bar {
      display: flex;
      height: 24px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .dist-seg {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: white;
      transition: width 0.3s;
    }

    .pattern-history-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .pattern-history-table th {
      text-align: left;
      color: var(--text2);
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 6px 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .pattern-history-table td {
      padding: 5px 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    .pattern-history-table tr:hover td { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }

    /* Match list */
    .match-list { max-height: 300px; overflow-y: auto; }
    .match-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    }
    .match-row .teams { color: var(--text); }
    .match-row .score { font-weight: 600; }
    .match-row .season { color: var(--text2); font-size: 0.7rem; }

    /* Empty/loading */
    .empty-state {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      color: var(--text2);
    }
    .empty-state .big { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }

    /* Help */
    .help-note {
      background: rgba(168,85,247,0.1);
      border: 1px solid var(--purple);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text2);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .help-note code {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding: 1px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: var(--text2);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .toast {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      background: var(--card);
      color: var(--text);
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      display: none;
      z-index: 100;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      animation: fadeIn 0.3s;
    }
    .toast.show { display: block; }
    .toast.success { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent2); }
    .toast.error { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <header>
    <h1>⚽ YouGamble2</h1>
    <p>Premier League Pattern Analyzer — Custom IF→THEN Logic Engine</p>
    <div class="subtitle">2006–2026 · 20 seasons · 7,600+ matches</div>
  </header>

  <!-- Controls -->
  <div class="controls">
    <div class="control-card">
      <h3>① Select Team</h3>
      <select id="teamSelect"><option value="">— Choose a team —</option></select>
      <div style="margin-top:4px;font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--text2)">
        Data range: <span id="dataRange">2006–2026 (20 seasons)</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="control-card">
      <h3>② Select Season Range</h3>
      <div class="control-row">
        <label>From:</label>
        <select id="seasonFrom"></select>
        <label>To:</label>
        <select id="seasonTo"></select>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-primary btn-sm" id="btnLoadTeam">🔍 Analyze Team</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tabs -->
  <div class="tabs">
    <div class="tab-btn active" data-tab="patterns">📊 Pattern Analysis</div>
    <div class="tab-btn" data-tab="builder">🔧 Pattern Builder</div>
    <div class="tab-btn" data-tab="saved">💾 Saved Patterns</div>
    <div class="tab-btn" data-tab="matches">📅 Match History</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Saved patterns bar -->
  <div id="savedPatternsBar"></div>

  <!-- Tab: Pattern Analysis -->
  <div class="tab-content active" id="tab-patterns">
    <div id="patternResults">
      <div class="empty-state">
        <div class="big">👆</div>
        <p>Select a team and click <strong>Analyze Team</strong> to start.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px;font-size:0.8rem;color:var(--text2)">
          Then use the built-in rules or create your own in <strong>Pattern Builder</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tab: Pattern Builder -->
  <div class="tab-content" id="tab-builder">
    <div class="help-note">
      <strong>🛠 Custom Pattern Builder</strong> — Define your own IF→THEN rules.<br>
      Example: <em>"If Arsenal scored <strong>&lt; 1 goal</strong> in <strong>3 consecutive</strong> games, what happened in the 4th game?"</em>
    </div>

    <div class="controls" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
      <div class="control-card">
        <h3>Condition (IF)</h3>
        <div class="control-row">
          <select id="builderMetric">
            <option value="scored">Goals Scored</option>
            <option value="conceded">Goals Conceded</option>
            <option value="total">Total Goals (scored+conceded)</option>
            <option value="margin">Goal Margin</option>
            <option value="result">Match Result</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="control-row" id="builderCompareRow">
          <select id="builderCompare">
            <option value="lt">&lt; (less than)</option>
            <option value="lte">≤ (less or equal)</option>
            <option value="eq">= (equal to)</option>
            <option value="gte">≥ (greater or equal)</option>
            <option value="gt">&gt; (greater than)</option>
          </select>
          <label>Value:</label>
          <input type="number" id="builderValue" value="1" min="0" max="20" />
        </div>
        <div id="builderResultRow" class="control-row" style="display:none;">
          <select id="builderResult">
            <option value="win">Won</option>
            <option value="draw">Drew</option>
            <option value="loss">Lost</option>
            <option value="not_loss">Didn't Lose (Won/Drew)</option>
            <option value="not_win">Didn't Win (Drew/Lost)</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="control-row">
          <label>for <strong>consecutive</strong> matches:</label>
          <input type="number" id="builderConsecutive" value="3" min="1" max="20" style="width:60px;margin-bottom:0;" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="controls" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
      <div class="control-card">
        <h3>Analysis (THEN)</h3>
